  <brief_title>Efficacy/Safety of Amlodipine Plus Losartan Versus Losartan in Patients With Essential Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, 8-week, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Amlodipine 5mg+Losartan 100mg Versus Losartan 100mg in Patients With Essential Hypertension Not Controlled on Losartan Monotherapy</official_title>
