  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate of efficacy and safety of amlodipine plus losartan
      and losartan alone in patients with essential hypertension inadequately controlled on
      losartan monotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
